headline: GE HealthCare, Vernova, Aerospace Stocks All Tank on China's Retaliatory Tariffs
summary: Shares of the companies spun off from the former industrial icon General Electric were all tanking Friday, led by medical device maker GE HealthCare, on investor fears that they would be hurt by Beijing’s retaliatory levies countering President Donald Trump’s tariffs.
